- Combine table and dictionary processing into a single loop
- Replace atomic counters with thread-local counters

4. Selected Optimization:
The highest impact change would be to use emplace with std::move when inserting ASTs into the file_names map, since:
- AST objects are large and expensive to copy
- We're already storing them by pointer, so move is safe
- This eliminates unnecessary copying during map insertion

